Map by: SkinHead... AKA Goddaz... AKA SlapHead... AKA Slappy_991 :)

This is a kind of fun map with many explosive barrels to shoot :)

It kind of turns into a lag feste when the bomb explodes but thats only for like 2 seconds...

Includes: 
2 working small elevators & 2 working blast doors 


Ct: Have to stop the terroists from destroying the porty thing =/ :)

T: Destroy the porty thing =/ :)
